  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 44ff468522a88594f835ce1750834844, type: 3}
  m_Name: Combat3Intro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogue:
  - Of course, it would be irresponsible piloting to just sit there and let the enemy
    attack you.
  - When you are about to take a hit, you have some reactions available to you.
  - Let's try it now with this other enemy.
  - On your turn, you can press the Space button to yield all remaining actions and
    end your turn.
  - Skip this next turn so the enemy can try to hit you.
